title: [Midrian's Dyes, Front Room]
description: Sunlight trickles through white lace curtains and reflects off of several bottles arranged in tidy rows upon a long table set under the window.  Wide bookcases line the western wall, their shelves filled with bottles and vials of various shapes and sizes, while a carefully arranged oak bench sits at an angle to the northeastern wall.
